            <title>[SOLR-2545] Allow equals-sign in key of external file field</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-2545</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The external file field doesn&apos;t allow an equals-sign in the key. Instead of going through the hassle of escaping, this patch just uses lastIndexOf to get the float value.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
